    cito:cites <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053420> ;
    dc:creator "Grall, Elena; Jäger, Peter" ;
    dc:title "Nesticella Lehtinen & Saaristo 1980" ;
    trt:augmentsTaxonConcept <http://taxon-concept.plazi.org/id/Animalia/Nesticella_Lehtinen_1980> ;
    trt:publishedIn <http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4085.2.5> ;
    a trt:Treatment .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4085.2.5>
    dc:creator "Grall, Elena; Jäger, Peter" ;
    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "Four new species of the spider genus Nesticella Lehtinen & Saaristo, 1980 from Laos, Thailand and Myanmar and the first description of the male of Nesticella yui Wunderlich & Song, 1995 with a proposed new diagnostic character for the family Nesticidae Simon, 1894 (Arachnida, Araneae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053420> .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1053420>
    dc:description "FIGURES 33 – 39. Leg setae with pipette setae of tibia IV of Nesticella beccus n. sp. (33 – 34) and Nesticus eremita (35 – 39). 33, Sexual dimorphism of leg setae; arrows pointing to pipette setae. 34, Pipette setae and tactile setae. 35, Pipette setae. 36, Pipette seta (left), tactile seta (centre), trichobothrium (right). 37, Tactile setae (long) and pipette setae (short). 38 – 39, Pipette seta, details (34 – 39, showing males). Photo credits: 34, 37 – 39, Rainer Foelix, 35 – 36, Rainer Foelix and Bruno Erb." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1053420/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

